## Additional Notes

This curriculum material was created with the assistance of Claude AI by Anthropic.
The educational content, structure, and code examples have been reviewed and curated
for use by the developer community.

While AI assisted in creating this material, the knowledge, patterns, and practices
described here are based on established Go programming best practices, industry
standards, and official Go documentation.

